A Lone Elephant Attack is considered a very safe and cautious strategy and it was by far the most popular during the early years of Arimaa.  As the name suggests, this attack requires only a single piece while the rest of the army stays behind.  If both players employ the Lone Elephant Attack, it is known as a Dual Lone Elephant game.
