{{Featured book}}
<noinclude>{{print version|AQA A-Level Computing Unit 2|A-level Computing/AQA/Print_version/Unit_2‎}}
</noinclude>
This is a book about A-Level Computing. It aims to fit in with the [http://filestore.aqa.org.uk/subjects/specifications/alevel/AQA-2510-W-SP-14.PDF AQA GCE A-Level Computing] syllabus but is not endorsed by AQA. It should be useful as a revision guide or to find alternative explanations to the ones in your textbook. If you haven't heard of an A-Level then this book probably won't be of much interest to you but you can find out about them at [[w:A-Level|Wikipedia]].

If any part of this book ''is'' unclear or even wrong then please post a comment on the discussion page or simply fix it yourself! In particular, please say if the book assumes any knowledge or skills which not all A-Level Computing students have.
